{"tid":435981,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［世紀爭議］你地叫開「爆谷」定「炮谷」？","createTime":"2017-10-14T18:00:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-15T08:08:17.000Z","uid":96628,"like":6,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"13030562a86cc096173427f641fd8dd828ea51dd","tid":435981,"uid":96628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T18:00:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 炮谷<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 爆谷<br />\n<br />\n話說正話同啲兵去睇戲，<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 兵<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 職員<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔該炮谷餐<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 先生一個爆谷餐飲咩汽水？仲有冇其他<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我要「炮」谷餐<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望透過足球，讓孩子們改變對人事物的態度，有機會翻轉自己的人生<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我家住南港，他們全部都住我家！免錢啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 南韓隊已經第10次打世界盃了？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 餵唔收錢呀？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝，廿五個半啦。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁貴嘅？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 加底吖嘛。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 噉唔加底呢？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 三呀六個八啦。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔加底重貴過加底？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 哦，唔加底十二個二吖。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 噉加底呢？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 三十六個八咯。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 頭先又話廿五個半？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啊，系，廿五個半啦。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今朝早餐賣咩呀？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咩話？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今朝早餐賣乜嘢？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 火腿蛋囉。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幾錢呀？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 十二個二囉。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 加底呢？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 二十五個半囉。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 乜早餐都有加底嘅咩？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 噉你加兩條腸都得嘅。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 噉我加夠三條腸要幾多錢呀？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好啦。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幾多錢呀？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我係送外賣架咋。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我問你幾多錢呀！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我唔知呀。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幾多錢！"},{"pid":"55655fac7acce6a94e069f7a758ca06eb43335e3","tid":435981,"uid":86756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T18:02:01.000Z","msg":"樓豬你想點撚樣?"},{"pid":"43226c3caf9875fd87d60c5ab08ae277a5f2983f","tid":435981,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T18:02:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓豬你想點撚樣?</blockquote>"},{"pid":"2c8527027e7e2e471c592f37baa51421f14f8163","tid":435981,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T18:02:41.000Z","msg":"樓豬你想點撚樣?"},{"pid":"ca9d52dab4d04f66192e4b84701167dda57bf849","tid":435981,"uid":12032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T18:59:58.000Z","msg":"樓豬你想點撚樣?"},{"pid":"a6f804b98f291c3bdcaec176f31ad9ee922e7616","tid":435981,"uid":52839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T19:01:37.000Z","msg":"系你老母 唔撚好笑呀"},{"pid":"cac590f21a080ede32239103625b7e24a0c96f3e","tid":435981,"uid":34852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T19:04:56.000Z","msg":"0分重作"},{"pid":"19b925d4f9df34aeebf4dc3cd5202c68d11503cb","tid":435981,"uid":3203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T19:07:04.000Z","msg":"你做乜撚嘢呀屌你老母"},{"pid":"c96f09866416c7a83e861d10a8c6f9bfbbaec9c2","tid":435981,"uid":18800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T08:08:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}